Title: Without (2)
Plot: As the search for Mulder intensifies in the Arizona desert, Gibson Praise leads Scully to believe that she is truly closer to her target. Meanwhile, A.D. Kersh informs Agent Doggett that he has been assigned as Mulder's successor on the X-Files.
GuestStars: Brian Thompson, Jonathan Palmer, Marc Gomes, Christine Firkins, Sal Landi, Jo-Ann Dean
